@EnrollmentSystem.AuthService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001

### Health Check
GET {{EnrollmentSystem.AuthService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Login (Student)
POST {{EnrollmentSystem.AuthService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student1",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login (Faculty)
POST {{EnrollmentSystem.AuthService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "faculty1",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Validate Token (Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login response)
GET {{EnrollmentSystem.AuthService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/validate
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Accept: application/json

###

### Logout (Replace YOUR_TOKEN_HERE with actual token from login response)
POST {{EnrollmentSystem.AuthService_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

